196
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:47,910
no matter how far,

197
00:12:49,050 --> 00:12:50,430
it'll just be us two brothers

198
00:12:50,430 --> 00:12:51,630
traveling together.

199
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,100
